Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.79,0:00:11.79,Style1,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Môžeš mi vrátiť telo späť do normálu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.00,0:01:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak si to želáš, otec...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kazuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.51,0:01:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo si želáš ty?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Byť s tebou, otec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čoskoro bude po všetkom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.72,0:02:33.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Epizóda 24\NLegenda
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je koniec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetko prebehlo ako v snoch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je druhá budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mal si dve budúcnosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.27,0:03:20.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stať sa Kamuim Drakov nebies alebo zeme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.27,0:03:21.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To bola jedna vec,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.87,0:03:26.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ktorú nevedeli ani jasnovidci ako princezná Hinoto a ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Avšak je jedno, ktorú stranu by si si vybral,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui Drakov zeme porazí Kamuiho Drakov nebies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a zmení svet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.12,0:03:39.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je jedna nemenná budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.42,0:03:45.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vtedy si sa rozhodol stať sa Drakom nebies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že si si vybral.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.07,0:03:55.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť jedného zo Siedmych pečatí, Drakov nebies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vybral si si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo je to s tebou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak sa staneš Drakom nebies,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,mojím osudom je stať sa Drakom zeme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.08,0:04:07.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-O čom to hovoríš, Fuma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dva Posvätné meče...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dve budúcnosti...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som tvoje hviezdne dvojča.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som druhý "Kamui"!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vybral si si ťažký osud,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,keďže si sa rozhodol stať sa Drakom nebies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prišiel si o tých, ktorých si miloval...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.84,0:04:34.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stratil si kamarátov, ktorým si veril...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A zakaždým bolo tvoje srdce roztrhané na kusy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keby si si vybral byť Drakom zeme,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:45.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,aspoň by si nebol roztrhaný na kusy smútkom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.49,0:04:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale ak by to tak bolo, tú bolesť by cítil Fuma, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tak potom som spokojný so svojou voľbou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.33,0:05:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak by som mal s Fumom vymenené osudy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.07,0:05:07.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,určite by sa aj on pokúsil priviesť ma späť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Asi máš pravdu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma ma volá.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okrem teba
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,všetkých Sedem pečatí stratilo ich silu tvoriť bariéry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bariérové kamene mrakodrapov v Shinjuku,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sunshine 60,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,spleť bariér tvorená traťou Yamamote,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokijská stanica,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dúhový most,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,budova parlamentu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.24,0:05:43.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už z nich ostali len prázdne schránky.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.85,0:05:47.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Posledné miesto, posledná bariéra, ktorá ešte ostala...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.98,0:05:50.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď tá padne...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Viem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale najskôr
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,zabijem Fumu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui Drakov nebies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nemôže vyhrať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kakyou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hokuto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stále môžeme niečo urobiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuzuriha, niekto za tebou prišiel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arashi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáč,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,že som zranila niekoho, na kom ti veľmi záleží.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.35,0:07:30.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie, chápem, ako sa cítiš, Arashi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prezident mi pred chvíľou povedal,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,že Sorata zomrel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcela si ochrániť Soratu, niekoho, na kom ti veľmi záležalo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kusanagi to určite pochopí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Najťažšie je
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nebyť schopný ochrániť niekoho, na kom ti veľmi záleží.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuzuriha...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcela som zmeniť osud,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ale nedokázala som nič zmeniť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ani jedinú vec...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arashi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.99,0:08:09.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Možno nemôžeme zmeniť osud.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale tam vonku je stále niekto, kto sa snaží bojovať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetci sme už stratili naše sily Drakov nebies,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ale stále si môžeme niečo želať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo si mám želať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už nič nemám...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To, čo si želal Sorata.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myslím, že Sorata sa ťa snažil chrániť
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a aj svet, v ktorom žiješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.46,0:08:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Karen a Daisuke si želali niečo podobné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To si myslím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arashi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.23,0:08:54.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetko teraz leží na Kamuiho pleciach.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:57.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Verme mu a želajme si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.95,0:09:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nechala som sa sem niekým preniesť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,pretože som chcela s tebou hovoriť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:36.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To, čo som urobila Seiovi, ťa zranilo ešte viac, ako keby som to neurobila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.85,0:09:41.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A urobila som to pre vás oboch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moje želanie sa nesplnilo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je to vážne ťažké, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nemôžeš ostať takýto navždy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.26,0:09:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sei a ja už nežijeme v tvojom svete,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:01.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ale sme v tvojom srdci, Subaru.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spomeň si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ešte stále musí byť niečo, čo chceš ochrániť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozmýšľaj!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo si urobil?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ty, jasnovidec, dúfaš v inú budúcnosť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nateraz ťa nechám žiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.73,0:10:31.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretože ti musím ukázať budúcnosť, po ktorej netúžiš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aký biedny svet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zem si želá zmenu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.03,0:11:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ty si jediný, kto tomu stojí v ceste.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je zbytočné bojovať proti osudu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,... ťa porazím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nemožné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To nemôže byť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dokiaľ ma budeš vyzývať k boji,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.55,0:13:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nikdy nebude tvojím osudom prebudiť sa ako Drak nebies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a tvojím osudom bude smrť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.75,0:13:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drak nebies, ktorý namieri Posvätný meč na toho, 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,koho chce chrániť, nemôže nikdy vypustiť jeho plnú silu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď si sa ma snažil poraziť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,vybral si si vlastnú porážku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui, nie je možné, aby si proti mne vyhral.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je jediná možná budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetky pečate boli zničené.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je to,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,čo si Zem
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,želá!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.54,0:14:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že jasnovidec Drakov zeme zišiel z cesty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale je to len otázka času.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď bude táto bariéra preč,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,zničenie sveta sa stane skutočnosťou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tvoja sila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.73,0:15:02.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sila, ktorú si si želal, ma sem priviedla.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale to je všetko, čo dokážem pre teba urobiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto nie je moja sila...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.91,0:15:12.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie je možné, aby som to zadržal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ty si jediný, kto dokáže urobiť zvyšok...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale ja už nemám...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ponoril som sa do tvojho vedomia,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.69,0:15:26.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,aby som sa pokúsil ťa priviesť späť do reality, spomínaš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.89,0:15:29.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Potom si sa vrátil z vlastnej vôle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.73,0:15:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ľutuješ to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Samozrejme, že to neľutujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tak to potom stačí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Musíš to tvoje želanie len dotiahnuť do konca...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,... všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.79,0:15:51.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.96,0:15:58.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bariéra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nič sa nezmenilo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nakoniec je len...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,... jedna budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je koniec, Kamui.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moje...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,... želanie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Verím ti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.12,0:16:30.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Že sa staneš silným a nič ťa neporazí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Staň sa silným.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aby si mohol ochrániť tých, ktorých máš rád.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.53,0:16:44.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale aj tak chcem v teba veriť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui, už si ľutoval dosť, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tak sa dívaj vpred a urob o krok viac než teraz!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.15,0:17:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť ešte nebola určená, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Draci nebies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,zomreli!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Konečne viem,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ako ťa priviesť späť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som Kamui Drakov zeme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.63,0:17:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcel som ochrániť teba a tento svet, v ktorom žiješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.07,0:17:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale dokážeš len zomrieť a zmiznúť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A svet uvidí revolúciu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nezmiznem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.68,0:18:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretože navždy ostanem v tvojom srdci.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.62,0:18:07.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Konečne som si to uvedomil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kotori žije vo mne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj mama...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj Sorata...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite bude ďalej žiť v Arashinom srdci.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.47,0:18:21.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hinoto, Saiki a aj Karen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetci žijú v srdciach druhých...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.17,0:18:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zverili svoje želania tým, ktorí ešte žijú...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takže ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,... zverím moje želanie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,... tebe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.62,0:18:39.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je budúcnosť, ktorú som si vybral.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.22,0:19:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je Kamuiho bariéra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui nás ochránil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Celý svet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.09,0:20:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že dievča, do ktorého sa zaľúbim, bude krásne!\N- Sorata
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.23,0:20:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finálny boj sa skončil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale iným spôsobom, než v mojich snoch.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.07,0:20:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ľudia zaťažení osudom, každý s vlastným želaním,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,zmizli bez toho, aby o tom verejnosť vedela.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.55,0:20:53.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale ich želania ostali nažive v srdciach tých, ktorých tu zanechali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A legenda pokračuje a je predávaná ďalej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.03,0:21:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť nebola jedna a absolútna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A odteraz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,bude toľko budúcností, koľko je želaní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.89,0:21:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kakyou!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tentokrát poďme naozaj.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Von.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.00,0:22:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O budúcnosti ešte nie je rozhodnuté, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.29,0:22:31.29,Style1,,0,0,0,,Preklad a časovanie: Dashio
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.29,0:22:34.29,Style1,,0,0,0,,Korekcia: Ayamee
